text: Kampong Mendaram Kecil (Malay for Mendaram Kecil Village) is a village in Belait District, Brunei, within the mukim of Labi. The postcode for Kampong Mendaram Kecil is KE3737. == See also == * List of villages in Brunei * Kampong Mendaram Besar == References == Mendaram Kecilc
title: Kampong Mendaram Kecil
